### 1. Login as Admin
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### Save token from response
@token = {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### 2. Get Dashboard Stats
GET http://localhost:8080/api/accounting/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Get Payment Reconciliation
POST http://localhost:8080/api/accounting/payment-reconciliation
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startDate": "2024-01-01",
  "endDate": "2024-12-31",
  "gateway": "ALL"
}

### 4. Import Reconciliation File (CSV)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/accounting/payment-reconciliation/import
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="reconciliation.csv"
Content-Type: text/csv

OrderCode,TransactionId,Amount,TransactionDate
ORD001,TXN123,1000000,2024-01-15T10:30:00
ORD002,TXN124,2000000,2024-01-16T14:20:00
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="gateway"

SEPAY
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### 5. Get Shipping Reconciliation
GET http://localhost:8080/api/accounting/shipping-reconciliation?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Get Financial Reports - Orders View
GET http://localhost:8080/api/accounting/reports?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31&viewMode=ORDERS
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Get Financial Reports - Daily View
GET http://localhost:8080/api/accounting/reports?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31&viewMode=DAILY
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Get Financial Reports - Monthly View
GET http://localhost:8080/api/accounting/reports?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31&viewMode=MONTHLY
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. Export Reports to Excel
GET http://localhost:8080/api/accounting/reports/export?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. Get All Periods
GET http://localhost:8080/api/accounting/periods
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11. Close Period (replace {id} with actual period ID)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/accounting/periods/1/close
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 12. Reopen Period (ADMIN only, replace {id} with actual period ID)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/accounting/periods/1/reopen
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

